<br>
From the very beginning I've had questions about this case.  After the birth of her fourth child Yates had post-partum depression so severe she tried to kill herself twice, and was warned by a doctor against having more kids.  So, one might wonder, what the hell was up with having the fifth child?  I have a feeling that's where the husband's support of her might come from -- guilt?<br>
<br>
After her fifth child, she not only had post-partum depression, she had post-partum psychosis (extremely rare, and far more serious than &quot;mere depression&quot;) and she sought mental health treatment for it -- but it appears she didn't receive appropriate treatment (there have been some news articles about what treatment she did receive, and I think there's an investigation of the psychiatrist who treated her).<br>
<br>
I'm not saying I have any sympathy whatsoever for her act of killing her children -- this was a horrible crime, and the jury will decide whether she's legally responsible for it -- but I really have to wonder about a situation where a woman whose problem was triggered by having children continued to have children, and who literally begged for help for her condition and didn't receive it.  This was a sad situation for years before it turned tragic.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/uanalornesongheart.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Analorne Songheart</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 244<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/19/02 9:47:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3066.topic&index=23>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Public Hangings?</span><hr size=1> Arikel said:<br>
