<br>
I can damn sure rant about it, though.  I'm a mother.  The very idea of watching one of my children squirm face down in a bathtub while drowning at the hands of someone they love and trust makes me physically ill.  It makes me angry.  It makes me want to wake my children up at midnight just to tell them I love them.  <br>
<br>
