<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
If my spouse killed my children we wouldn't have to worry about insanity pleas, capitol punishment, or anything else. I'd fucking kill that person so fast they wouldn't know what hit them. I certainly wouldn't be giving excuses for this person.<br>
